Dataset Name: Balance of Payments (BOP), World and Regional Aggregates
Balance of Payments (BOP), World and Regional Aggregates
Balance of Payments (BOP), World and Regional Aggregates
Metadata Value: BOPSY Global Tables aggregate country data by major balance of payments components and by international investment position (IIP) data for (i) Net IIP and (ii) Total Assets and Total Liabilities.  Data for countries, country groups, and the world are provided. In addition to data reported by countries as shown in BOPSY, balance of payments data are provided for international organizations in BOPSY Global Tables.  The BOPSY Global Tables include, in addition to reported data, data derived in a few instances indirectly from published sources.

Dataset Name: Balance of Payments (BOP), World and Regional Aggregates
Balance of Payments (BOP), World and Regional Aggregates
Metadata Value: In addition to the 195 countries covered by the Balance of Payments Statistics (BOP), the BOP World and Regional Aggregates database contains data for 11 regions (country groups) including the world.
